{
  "lesson": "WC-13-01",
  "audioMaster": "training/module13-reports-audit/WC-13-01-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 210.207,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Open the Reports module.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 1.495,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "Every figure a client asks you for starts here.",
      "startS": 2.001,
      "endS": 4.672,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "A hundred and seventy-three reports, already sorted so you're not digging through a folder.",
      "startS": 5.277,
      "endS": 9.902,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "The left sidebar is your way in.",
      "startS": 10.501,
      "endS": 12.4,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Start at the top of the sidebar.",
      "startS": 12.8,
      "endS": 14.397,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "These five shortcuts are pre-built slices of the same list.",
      "startS": 14.986,
      "endS": 18.405,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "The ones you starred, the ones running on a timer, the analytics set.",
      "startS": 18.715,
      "endS": 22.573,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "When a client wants what they always want, you skip the search and click the view.",
      "startS": 23.282,
      "endS": 27.263,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Below that, nineteen categories.",
      "startS": 27.68,
      "endS": 29.843,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "Financial, transactions, employee labor, inventory, and the rest,",
      "startS": 30.232,
      "endS": 30.917,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "each with a live count beside it.",
      "startS": 31.218,
      "endS": 33.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Some are broad, like transactions with twenty-one reports.",
      "startS": 33.643,
      "endS": 35.234,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Some hold just one, like weather.",
      "startS": 35.73,
      "endS": 37.384,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "This is how you turn a wall of reports into the two or three",
      "startS": 37.894,
      "endS": 41.38,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "that actually answer the question in front of you.",
      "startS": 41.865,
      "endS": 50,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "On the right, the list itself.",
      "startS": 50.465,
      "endS": 52.365,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "A search box sits above it.",
      "startS": 53.177,
      "endS": 54.709,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Type a few letters of a report's name and the list shrinks to match.",
      "startS": 55.253,
      "endS": 59.19,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Faster than paging through four screens when you already know what you're after.",
      "startS": 59.51,
      "endS": 63.44,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Top right, one button: Schedule Report.",
      "startS": 63.84,
      "endS": 66.241,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "That's how a report gets put on a timer and mailed out on its own.",
      "startS": 66.761,
      "endS": 70.279,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "We're only pointing at it today.",
      "startS": 70.647,
      "endS": 72.081,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "It sends, so we leave it alone.",
      "startS": 72.373,
      "endS": 74.281,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Now the columns.",
      "startS": 74.77,
      "endS": 75.874,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "A star for favorites, the report's name, its category, its type, and when it last ran.",
      "startS": 76.344,
      "endS": 77.766,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Five columns tell you what a report is and whether anyone has touched it lately.",
      "startS": 78.223,
      "endS": 88.24,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Look at the Type column.",
      "startS": 88.64,
      "endS": 90.026,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Standard, Scheduled, or Analytics.",
      "startS": 90.472,
      "endS": 93.004,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "A dash under Last Run means nobody has run it yet.",
      "startS": 93.771,
      "endS": 95.655,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "A date and time means someone did.",
      "startS": 95.962,
      "endS": 97.472,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "The daily financial, for instance, has a scheduled twin that last ran in late March.",
      "startS": 98.041,
      "endS": 100.061,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "And the starred rows are your favorites, one click away in that view up top.",
      "startS": 100.736,
      "endS": 109.946,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Click a report to open it.",
      "startS": 110.458,
      "endS": 111.861,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Take the daily financial.",
      "startS": 112.312,
      "endS": 113.577,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "The list steps aside and the report viewer takes over.",
      "startS": 114.769,
      "endS": 117.986,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "Same idea as opening a file: you picked it, now you're inside it.",
      "startS": 118.752,
      "endS": 122.488,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Across the top, the filters.",
      "startS": 122.96,
      "endS": 124.872,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "A location selector, a date range with a from and a to, and a More Filters button for the rest.",
      "startS": 125.357,
      "endS": 126.586,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "This is where you tell the report which sites and which days before you run it.",
      "startS": 126.95,
      "endS": 136.16,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Two buttons frame it.",
      "startS": 136.619,
      "endS": 137.75,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Run Report renders it.",
      "startS": 138.391,
      "endS": 139.784,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Close Report backs you out.",
      "startS": 140.42,
      "endS": 141.94,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Notice Schedule Report isn't here.",
      "startS": 142.667,
      "endS": 144.577,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "Scheduling stays on the hub; in here you only run and read.",
      "startS": 144.974,
      "endS": 148.866,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Click Run Report.",
      "startS": 149.28,
      "endS": 150.217,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "Summary tiles and a table build from the filters you set.",
      "startS": 150.217,
      "endS": 154.612,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "Running it only reads the numbers, so nothing is sent and nothing is saved.",
      "startS": 154.612,
      "endS": 159.609,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "In the drill, you'll hunt down the per-location and per-shift rows,",
      "startS": 159.609,
      "endS": 163.043,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "and the refund column, before you close it.",
      "startS": 163.043,
      "endS": 165.541,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Check the stamp on the result.",
      "startS": 166,
      "endS": 167.633,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "It carries the date the report was generated,",
      "startS": 168.202,
      "endS": 170.549,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "and in this demo it flags the figures as sample data.",
      "startS": 170.757,
      "endS": 173.984,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "On a real client tenant that same line reads their live numbers instead.",
      "startS": 174.977,
      "endS": 179.135,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "Done reading? Close Report.",
      "startS": 179.76,
      "endS": 181.55,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "The viewer folds away and the full list is back, exactly as you left it.",
      "startS": 182.367,
      "endS": 186.424,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "You ran a report and touched nothing.",
      "startS": 186.832,
      "endS": 188.793,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "That's the whole loop.",
      "startS": 189.2,
      "endS": 190.382,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "Find a report by view or category, open it,",
      "startS": 191.049,
      "endS": 193.139,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "set the location and the dates, run it, read it, close it.",
      "startS": 193.536,
      "endS": 194.068,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "When a client swears a report looks wrong, this is the screen you'll share with them.",
      "startS": 194.416,
      "endS": 196.027,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "Now you know every control on it,",
      "startS": 196.328,
      "endS": 196.749,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "and the next lesson takes you into the audit trail behind those numbers.",
      "startS": 197.082,
      "endS": 209.76,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}